title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_FirstTalk
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Now look at you.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Me?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
You think I'm talkin' to some other schmuck?
Don't you look cute. Tryna look tough in your lil' leather jacket?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightSound>>
Did you borrow that from your big brother?
You tryna start a lil' gang or somethin'?
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Sorta. Why? You wanna join?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Listen, I'm sure you're sweet n' all.
But I'm a grown woman.
I don't hang out with lil' boys.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
I'm no "little boy".
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
*She just smiles*
<<RightSound>>
Let me look at your gang, I'll make up my mind pretty quick.
<<SetGameBoolData TrueZeal_ShellyKFirstBarTalkDone true>>
<<SaveProgress>>
[[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_PartyCheck]]
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_PartyCheck
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<if CharacterInParty("Anton") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Anton]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("Bimini") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Bimini]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("Rags") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Rags]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("Thype") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Thype]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("Hans") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Hans]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("Pearl") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Pearl]]
<<elseif CharacterInParty("TrueZeal_ShellyK") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_ShellyK]]
<<elseif HasPartySpace() is false>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_PartySpace]]
<<endif>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Damn, some of you boys don't look half bad.
Sure, I'll head out with you all, but don't think we'll be makin' this a regular thing.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightSound>>
When this is done, I'm not comin' back for round two.
<<if CharacterInParty("Arnold") is true>>
    [[TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Complete]]
<<else>>
    <<HideRoomNPCs>>
    <<HireCharacter TrueZeal_ShellyK_CH>>
    <<SaveProgress>>
<<endif>>
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Anton
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the lil' pervert.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Anton?
<<LeftSet Anton>>
<<LeftSound>>
What? Nowak?!
<<LeftSound>>
Why do you assume that means me?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Because you're a pervy lil' freak.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
What? Babes love me.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<LeftSound>>
I've got charisma.
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Well this "babe" definitely doesn't.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Aww c'mon, get to know me a little.
*Anton puts his hands onto Shelly's lap*
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK>>
<<RightFocus>>
*Shelly violently shoves Anton away and draws her knife*
<<RightSound>>
Listen you snivellin' lil' abortion.
<<RightSound>>
Touch me again, and I'll shove your head so far up your own ass that when it finally slops back out you'll be the first jag off that's ever been miscarried twice.
<<LeftFocus>>
Hey... *Anton raises his hands in submission*
<<LeftSound>>
I'm in the business of listening to the perspectives of women.
So I just want you to know...
I understand and respect your position on this matter.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
...
*Anton leans into Nowak's ear and whispers*
<<LeftSet Anton TrueZeal_Sad>>
<<LeftSound>>
Nowak, please don't kick me out of the gang, I need this.
<<LeftSet Anton>>
<<LeftSound>>
Pretty please?
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Alright, Golden Boy, you gonna do the right thing?
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Bimini
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the sword girl.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Bimini? No, she's part of the team.
<<LeftSet Bimini>>
<<LeftSound>>
Hey, {"@#$%"} you lady, no one tells me to leave.
<<LeftSound>>
I carry this goddamn team.
These saps are nothing without me.
<<LeftSound>>
Right, Nowak?
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
Uhh... yeah, I guess.
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
See, I don't play nice with other girls.
So if you want me to tag along...
<<RightSound>>
Sword {"@#$%#"} has to go.
<<LeftSet Bimini>>
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
You {"@#$%"}ing {"@#$%"}, I'll kill you.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
That's cute...
<<LeftSet Devs>>
<<RightSet Devs>>
<<LeftFocus>>
*Bimini and Shelly K. continue to violently argue for some time*
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Rags
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the hag.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Who? Rags? But Rags is part of the team.
<<LeftSet Rags>>
<<LeftSound>>
I was leaving anyway.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
What?! Why?
<<LeftSet Rags>>
<<LeftSound>>
I've got things to do.
I don't need travelling companions.
Your whole group is pretty slow.
<<LeftSound>>
Sometimes not just physically...
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
Wait, wait-
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Sounds like the decision is pretty clear, Golden Boy.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Rags, are you sure you want to leave?
<<LeftSet Rags>>
<<LeftSound>>
Yeah.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
What if we pick up the pace?
<<LeftSet Rags>>
*She kinda just shrugs*
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
You gonna run after her, or is it time I join your lil' gang?
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Thype
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the monkey girl.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
What? Who?
*Nowak looks around*
<<LeftSet Bosch>>
<<LeftSound>>
I think she means Thype?
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
Do you mean Thype?
*Nowak points*
<<RightSet Thype>>
<<RightFocus>>
*Thype is eating something out of the bottom of an abandoned glass*
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightSound>>
Yeah, I don't play nice with other girls.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Thype isn't a girl.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
You sure about that, Golden Boy?
<<LeftFocus>>
I think so.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<LeftSound>>
Hey, Thype! You a girl?
<<RightSet Thype>>
<<RightFocus>>
*Thype contorts their fingers to spell the word "blood" back at Nowak*
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
...
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
I don't know what that means.
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Either way, she's too "girl" for my liking.
Make your call, Golden Boy.
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Hans
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the blue ball.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Hans? Why would I ditch Hans?
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
I don't like how she looks.
Besides, I don't play nice with other girls.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
But Hans is barely a girl, she's like a sponge thing.
<<LeftSet Hans TrueZeal_Surprised>>
*Despite still wearing the same mask, Hans looks a little sad at Nowak's comment*
<<LeftSound>>
Perhaps I hinder the efficiency of the pre-colonial mass.
<<LeftSound>>
If you feel the likelihood of success would be higher in my absence, you are welcome to excise me.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightFocus>>
*Shelly raises her eyebrows at Nowak*
<<LeftFocus>>
...
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Pearl
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
