title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_ShellyK
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Ditch the skinwalker.
<<LeftSet TrueZeal_ShellyK>>
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Yeah, I was meanin' to ask.
<<LeftSound>>
What is goin' on here exactly?
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<LeftSound>>
What? I thought you guys were twins or something.
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
I don't know anything about that.
<<LeftSet TrueZeal_ShellyK>>
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Well pour me a drink too, this whole situation's givin' me a headache.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Well, either way, Golden Boy; you definitely don't need two o' me.
===

title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Female
