title: TrueZeal_ShellyK_Bar_Complete
tags:
---
<<LeftSet Arnold>>
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Drink>>
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
No, I think you'll be coming back.
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Oh? And who are you?
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Why? Care enough to get to know me?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Hehe, I'll bite.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Oh I bet you do a lot more than that.
<<LeftSet Bosch>>
<<LeftSound>>
Nowak?
Nowak, what's happening?
<<LeftSet Arnold>>
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Oh careful lil' boy, don't play games if you don't know the rules.
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
Why don't you teach me then?
I'd love to learn how to play this game with you.
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Well, I think-
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Blush>>
*Shelly blushes*
<<LeftFocus>>
<<LeftSound>>
You think you might just stick around?
<<LeftSound>>
Think you might want to see the "rules" Mr. A can teach you about this little game of ours?
<<RightFocus>>
<<RightSound>>
Mr. A?
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Smirk>>
<<RightSound>>
Hehe, I like that.
*She extends her hand*
<<LeftFocus>>
*He kisses it gently and then matches her gaze*
<<RightSet TrueZeal_ShellyK Blush>>
*Suddenly he pulls her from her seat and into his arms*
<<LeftSound>>
Let's mosey on out, 'cause a little girl like you has a lot to learn from a man like me.
<<LeftSound>>
Wouldn't want to leave you here skipping class.
<<LeftSet Nowak>>
...
<<RightSet Arnold>>
<<RightFocus>>
*Arnold winks at Nowak*
<<RightSet Devs>>
<<LeftFocus>>
...
<<LeftSet Bosch>>
<<LeftSound>>
Wow, uhh.
Huh..
<<Unlock TrueZeal_ShellyK>>
<<HideRoomNPCs>>
<<HireCharacter TrueZeal_ShellyK_CH>>
<<SaveProgress>>
===

